description: This looks up the location of a given ip4 address. Make sure to spell out the IP address with four numbers separated by the word 'dot.' - So you might ask for "four dot four dot four dot four."
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask eye pee lookup where is four dot four dot four dot four
Alexa, ask eye pee lookup who is four dot four dot four dot four?
Alexa, ask eye pee lookup and lookup four dot four dot four dot four
name: IP Lookup
